      "rationale": "A three-level mesh convergence study was performed on the pedicle screw geometry. QoI (stiffness) changed by 2.1% between medium and fine meshes, and 0.8% between fine and extra-fine meshes. Richardson extrapolation applied; discretization error estimated at 1.4%. Required level 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
