      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative solver convergence criteria documented and residuals verified to be below tolerance thresholds.",
      "rationale": "Newton-Raphson nonlinear solver used with force residual tolerance 1e-4 and displacement residual tolerance 1e-5. Convergence verified for all 11 load cases. No divergence or non-convergence events observed. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
